{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/apa-itu-wota/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Apa Itu Wota?","content":"\n<p>Pernah denger wota gak? Bro sis, kalau kita berbicara tentang kebudayaan Jepang, tentunya gak akan jauh-jauh dari kata anime, manga, video game, musik, komik, drama dan sebagainya. Bagi kalian para penggemar anime dan manga, biasanya bakal disebut sebagai anime lovers atau manga lovers. Tapi kalian tahu nggak kalau ada satu lagi sebutan khusus bagi penggemar idol-idol Jepang yang dikenal dengan sebutan wota.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17526\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17526\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : nulis.co.id)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : nulis.co.id)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-1.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-1.jpg\" alt=\"(from : nulis.co.id)\" class=\"wp-image-17526\"/><figcaption>(from : nulis.co.id)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Wota itu sebenernya asal katanya dari kata otaku. Seperti yang kalian tahu, otaku sendiri sering digambarkan sebagai orang yang gak mau bersosialisasi alias demen hidup di dunianya sendiri. Tetapi seiring berjalannya waktu, konotasi otaku pun berubah dan ditulis sebagai wotaku untuk membedakan arti otaku yang dulu dengan yang sekarang. Kata wotaku kemudian disingkat dan lebih dikenal dengan sebutan wota.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17529\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17529\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : ridhofumi.blogspot.id)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : ridhofumi.blogspot.id)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-2.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-2.jpg\" alt=\"(from : ridhofumi.blogspot.id)\" class=\"wp-image-17529\"/><figcaption>(from : ridhofumi.blogspot.id)<br></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"720\" height=\"405\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/b7h4oj0XuzI\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17532\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17532\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Wota 3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : motretjkt48.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-3.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-3.jpg\" alt=\"(from : motretjkt48.com)\" class=\"wp-image-17532\"/><figcaption>(from : motretjkt48.com)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Wota adalah sebuah istilah yang merujuk kepada fans dari J-pop idol, yang terkadang melakukan semacam tarian khusus pemberi semangat, yang dikenal sebagai wotagei.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Arti lainnya yaitu orang-orang yang mempunyai dedikasi tinggi untuk mendukung dan mengikuti perkembangan idol-idol mereka. Antusiasme dan obsesi yang mereka punya lebih tinggi dari seorang fans. Bahkan seorang wota tidak akan pernah ragu untuk mengorbankan dirinya mulai dari mengesampingkan harga dirinya, menghamburkan uangnya, dan membuang waktunya demi untuk mendukung idolnya tersebut.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17535\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17535\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : akb48.co.jp)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : akb48.co.jp)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-4.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-4.jpg\" alt=\"(from : akb48.co.jp)\" class=\"wp-image-17535\"/><figcaption>(from : akb48.co.jp)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17538\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17538\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : nogizaka46.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : nogizaka46.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-5.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-5.jpg\" alt=\"(from : nogizaka46.com)\" class=\"wp-image-17538\"/><figcaption>(from : nogizaka46.com)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tingkahnya cukup ekstrim hingga membuat mereka begitu peduli pada sang idola. Bahkan saking cintanya pada sang idola, di Jepang ada yang sampai bunuh diri saat mengetahui sang idolanya berpacaran atau menikah. Tindakan ekstrim semacam itulah yang membuat banyak orang menganggap wota adalah sesuatu yang negatif karena terlalu obsesif.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17541\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17541\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-6.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-6.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-6.jpg\" alt=\"(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)\" class=\"wp-image-17541\"/><figcaption>(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17544\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17544\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-7.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-7.jpg\" alt=\"(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)\" class=\"wp-image-17544\"/><figcaption>(from : beastthedoom.blogspot.id)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ciri-ciri lain, ia pasti punya semua album lagu-lagu idolnya, banyak banget tempelan poster idolnya yang memenuhi seluruh kamarnya, sering melakukan teriakan-teriakan dan gerakan-gerakan khusus seperti menari ketika menonton performance idol kecintaannya, selalu memakai kaos bergambar idolnya, suka pergi ke event-event tertentu untuk mendukung idol-nya dan banyak lagi. Bahkan ada juga yang membuat sendiri kue ulang tahun untuk merayakan hari ulang tahun idolnya dan merayakannya sendirian.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17547\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17547\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : celebrity.okezone.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : celebrity.okezone.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-8.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-8.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-8.jpg\" alt=\"(from : celebrity.okezone.com)\" class=\"wp-image-17547\"/><figcaption>(from : celebrity.okezone.com)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sementara itu di Indonesia, banyak orang yang gak tahu dan menganggap wota itu adalah sebutan nama Fans JKT48. Padahal sama sekali bukan. Wota itu hanya sebutan untuk fans-fans yang memiliki dedikasi tinggi untuk para idola mereka. Berarti selama ini banyak dari kita yang salah sebut dong yah.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17550\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17550\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : fansjkt48project.blogspot.id)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : fansjkt48project.blogspot.id)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-9.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-9.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-9.jpg\" alt=\"(from : fansjkt48project.blogspot.id)\" class=\"wp-image-17550\"/><figcaption>(from : fansjkt48project.blogspot.id)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk grup idol ini, pada umumnya gak ada nama khusus untuk fans mereka. Bagi JKT48 sebutan fans ya cuma &#8216;fans&#8217;, bukan wota. Buktinya salah satu majalah remaja terkenal &#8220;Hai&#8221; pernah menggelar polling untuk mencirikan jenis-jenis dan tingkatan fans JKT48. Ternyata didapatkan bahwa para fans berat mereka menyebut diri mereka sebagai Pendengar Setia JKT48, Fans Beratnya, Die Hard Fans!, Fans Kelas Menengah, dan terakhir Fans Biasa Saja. Banyak juga ya. Hehe</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-17553\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"17553\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-itu-wota/attachment/wota-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : kapanlagi.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : kapanlagi.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-10.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-10.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Wota-10.jpg\" alt=\"(from : kapanlagi.com)\" class=\"wp-image-17553\"/><figcaption>(from : kapanlagi.com)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Pada dasarnya mau itu fans ataupun wota tujuannya sama, yakni mensupport idolanya. Jadi jangan berhenti dukung grup idol yang kalian suka ya guys. Meskipun ada istilah ini, bukan berarti pendukung suatu grup idol itu 100% wota. Sebagai sesama penggemar, kita harus saling menghargai dan saling menghormati.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"387a23c1-c7b5-55a0-8db0-e63a192336f0"}}}